name: SerialNumbers
desc: An object that contains serial numbers for the updatable passes on a device.

items.name: serialNumbers
items.desc: An array of serial numbers for the updated passes.

items.name: lastUpdated
items.desc: A developer-defined string that contains a tag that indicates the modification time for the returned passes. You use the value of this key for the previousLastUpdated parameter of Get the List of Updatable Passes to return passes modified after the represented date and time.
